data.description: This stunning 2 bedrooms, 2 1/5 bath, one car garage townhouse is located in a friendly community with access to amenities, shopping and dinning. Buyer will enjoy sweeping views of the lush golf course from the backyard. This home features two well appointed primary bedroom suites with recently upgraded bathrooms.  This home embodies the perfect blend of comfort, style and beauty.
